# Vercel CLI upload exclusions for AgentTrust monorepo.
# Vercel projects link from repo root with Root Directory configured
# (web/ for agenttrust-web, docs-site/ for agenttrust-docs-site).
# docs-site prebuild reads parent files (mcp/CHANGELOG.md,
# trustgate/sdk/CHANGELOG.md, examples/attestor-demo/*.json), so we
# can't exclude sibling workspaces wholesale — only heavy artifacts.

# Solana / Anchor / Rust local-only artifacts (Unix sockets in
# .anchor/test-ledger crash the uploader without this).
.anchor/
target/
test-ledger/

# Node / Next / TS build outputs
node_modules/
.next/
.turbo/
dist/
build/

# Python / venv
.venv/
__pycache__/

# OS / editor / logs
.DS_Store
*.log

# Internal docs and plan dirs (do not ship to Vercel)
docs/plan/
docs/internal/
docs/research/
docs/references/
references/
plan/
research/
agenttrust-grant/

# Local-only workspaces not deployed via Vercel (kept out of Vercel uploads
# to keep them lean, but only for projects that don't need them).
# NOTE: do not exclude `status-page/` here — it has its own Vercel project
# rooted at status-page/ and needs its source uploaded with the monorepo.
migrations/
